Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To grant my wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:11.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,From seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:20.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.91,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:33.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.31,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:30.15,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(906,376)}Their Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.75,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Two eggs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:22.67,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.81,news,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer management \Nfunds to be increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Soft-boiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:26.81,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.99,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to get dressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.86,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you aren't going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Late? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.36,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.18,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the opening ceremony today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it's still August.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.28,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's earlier than in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.77,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd know, since it's \Nthe same as in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Can you toast the bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.68,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Komiya Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.40,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You should smile a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.88,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The eggs weren't even soft-boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You said whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:45.51,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:57.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:03.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't have time, thanks to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.72,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the lost child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't a tourist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.82,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I just moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know which class you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.02,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't too many people \Ngoing from this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.45,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.78,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Komiya Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.55,sora-main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone, be good to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.06,sora-main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya-san, your seat is in the \Nvery back of the second row.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:26.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.78,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You could have said \Nsomething if you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.96,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:48.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We met by the lake before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.60,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know why \Nyou said what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nonoka done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya-san, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.81,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Koharu, too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.38,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live by the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but it's more towards the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:42.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So in the morning—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true what you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really just move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:05.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mizusaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me straight up what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:46.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, two fresh ginger ales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:53.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're continuing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You might not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but it was a huge mess seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on the news, \Nso I kind of remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, around that time, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Some things you just have \Nto be there to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:25.16,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,A saucer just showed up out of \Nnowhere and parked at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yet no one even cares anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:34.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Our drinks are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that saucer caused—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think the townspeople mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They're all being fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:10.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just been pretending to \Nsit there for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it really up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:20.14,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The town's safety is more \Nand more at risk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.41,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something about \Nit before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think the town's as safe as it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer versus a friend in need,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:35.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a friend in need, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:40.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, let's take \Nback the town's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:53.00,Saucer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Saucer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooperation, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take back our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:11:02.26,Palace,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:11:02.26,Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooperation, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nonoka, you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You have to shout louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.89,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise they won't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.89,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.68,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooperation, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drive out the saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We do not need a saucer in our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We must stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Until the saucer goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:50.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can get rid of it, \Nwith everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.99,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:06.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.57,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:16.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,B?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we running?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:40.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because we didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should explain properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. We've been friends \Nsince we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know her really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.45,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,For coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It just kind of happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to our next plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.00,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.98,Management,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer Management
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.98,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.10,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're here about the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.08,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please fill out this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.11,Form,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Opinions regarding \Nsaucer management.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to meet straight with \Nthe person in charge of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk to the leaders—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:30.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:37.16,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk straight to the leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.29,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to your leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call for the \Nleaders at a reception desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:57.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be able to get to that \Nisland on a tour boat, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:03.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's off limits, \Nbecause it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.36,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.55,Saucer2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.55,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.01,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't get mad at Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.83,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,A weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.57,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.80,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.29,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you not to cause people trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:47.65,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's something pointless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.93,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing something so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.32,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the saucer and that girl's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.08,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, exchange student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.32,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.40,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Or nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Get me my backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:08.88,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:18.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're mad at me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:07.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to get rid \Nof the saucer so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago, the saucer came,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,and things changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:22.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some things that \Nhaven't gone back to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:28.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They used to launch \Nfireworks from the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:38.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but the fireworks were really \Npretty shining on the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:43.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But they stopped doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's launch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This works, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's launch this rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.63,sora-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get rid of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But nothing dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to find more \Npeople to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.62,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.64,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad should have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.33,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:45.84,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, have you been keeping \Nyour promise to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.64,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.48,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.26,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.86,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Something I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:20.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:24.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, leave it to me! \NWhat do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We want to make the \Nsaucer leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:33.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, do you hate the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:39.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to help my friend somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:44.53,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial \NMethod{\i0}: "Where Memories Live."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.43,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:42.94,sora-next-ep,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Where Memories Live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.94,sora-next-ep,,0000,0000,0000,,
